8. d5 Qb6
{ This is a super cool move for those who would like to enter chess history by producing a Morphian masterpiece.   The idea is to accelerate development and exploit the exposed King, ignoring material considerations in the process.   Stockfish prefers the immediate  8...Bb4+  9.Nc3  Ne4  .  Or  8...Ne5  as covered here. }
9. dxc6 Bb4+ 10. Nc3 O-O
{ And Black has tremendous compensation for the piece. The Rooks' entry into the attack will paralyze the White army in the abundance of pins. }
