8. Qg3 Nxe4 9. Nxe4 Rxe4 10. Bf4
{ This move is known to theory, but the engine already gives us a whopping -1.2, indicating that White's position is going downhill already! }
10... Qf6
{ The queen stands really well here, defending the kingside and aiming at the white king at the same time. }
