{ 11.Bxc7??  d6!  12.Bxd6  Qh6+!  The point! White loses a piece now.  13.Kb1  Bxd6  14.Rxd6  Qxd6-+  . White can't take the queen because of the back-rank mate! }
11... d6 12. Bd3 Nd4
{ This lovely idea and the subsequent moves signal a dangerous attack. White is in trouble! }
