{ The Spaniard is fighting in the spirit of the bravest toreadors. The attack is now in full swing, and it is aesthetically pleasing that all developed black pieces are hanging! }
15. bxa3
{ 15.Bc1  Qxf3  16.gxf3  Re7  17.Ng5  Nxc1  18.Rxc1  Bc5  leads to a completely winning endgame for Black. }
