Bxe4 Bxg2
{ This sensational strike is the culmination of the sparkling attack: Black emerges with material extra. }
20. Qxg2 Qxf4+ 21. Kb2 Nxe4
{ Time to take stock: Black has 3 pawns and a knight for a rook and White's king is severely exposed. The rest is simple: }
22. Rd4 Qf6 23. Qxe4 c5 24. Re1 h5 25. Qf4 Qxd4+ 26. Qxd4 cxd4 27. Re7 b6 28.
a4 g5 29. Kb3 Kg7 30. Rc7 Re8 31. Rxa7 Re2 32. Rb7 Rxf2 33. Rxb6 Rxh2 34. a5
Re2 35. a6 Re8 36. a7 Ra8 { Bravo Senor Vallejo, that was a stunner! } *

