1. e4 e5 2. Nc3 Nf6 3. f4 d5 4. fxe5 Nxe4 5. Nf3 Bc5 6. d4 Bb4 7. Bd2 c5 8.
Bb5+ Nc6 9. O-O O-O 10. Bxc6 bxc6 11. Nxe4 dxe4 12. Bxb4 cxb4 13. Ne1 f5
{ This move is the deviation from our theory, which is Ba6.   That said, f5 is part of our main plan and as such, it is a perfectly fine move. Black is already ahead, as the e1 Knight is having a rough time! }
